-t%E1%BB%ADu-gia-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-XBPOvpTlkXfBzRcRGDz99Q">Quá tửu gia kỳ 3 - 過酒家其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%ADch/author-0g7JqAcYihMIfY-BKbTDYA">Vương Tích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Quan-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-Minh-Trai-T%E1%BB%A5c-T%E1%BB%AB-Th%E1%BB%A9c-truy%E1%BB%87n-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-3-Ngh%C4%A9-Gi%C3%A1ng-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-%C4%91%C3%A1p-kim-m%C3%A3-kh%C3%A1ch/poem-FZpkfzKOnYF7rmZDs_dHNQ">Quan đệ Minh Trai “Tục Từ Thức truyện” ngẫu thành kỳ 3 - Nghĩ Giáng Hương phụng đáp kim mã khách - 觀弟明齊續徐式傳偶成三－擬絳香奉答金馬客</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%91i-Qu%E1%BB%B3nh/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-Thi%E1%BA%BFt-Nhai-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-tu%C3%BD-ca/poem-zJHP1Nu_WXThiVc4VkIRqg">Thứ vận Thiết Nhai tiên sinh tuý ca - 次韻鐵崖先生醉歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%91i-Qu%E1%BB%B3nh/author-xiBFy5bXgpv8FC-1c8m5xA">Bối Quỳnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-L%C6%B0u-%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-4IlbT4s56fn07bSG8HmYCA">Thượng Lưu Điền hành - 上留田行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ca/poem-HcukUJv5qKyrumSIpdzS2A">Tương Dương ca - 襄陽歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br></div>	</div>
